itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"我想知係咩原因導致到佢地會做成internal reflection of waves <br />\n係咪因爲提子皮佢有特別既構造而可以reflect waves <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:06:18.000Z","msg":"你上面條友唔識亂咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nA grape is the right size and <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">refractive</span></span> index to trap microwaves inside it.<br />\n<br />\nReflection 同 Refraction 係兩樣嘢嚟<br />\nn=c/v<br />\n<br />\n簡單講因為velocity of microwave in medium 慢咗所以先會trap住microwave<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Gwjzmn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Gwjzmn.png&h=ac276600&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2152af18923e64bede3d3538f60fea08cd30524b","tid":1031642,"uid":53254,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"試咗了...燒咗公司個pantry...而家成橦building走火警. 好彩公司冇cam, 希望冇人睇到我出入.<br />\n呢鑊多得連登仔唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e2359582ff47c9e3e0168471d4e10025c6150c","tid":1031642,"uid":167464,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會變綠色啫喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9da19fe38902ff0831e8fbf399efe0cae33521","tid":1031642,"uid":93062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"係咪因為有全內反射困住啲microwave<br />\n能量太大所以產生plasma"},{"pid":"183794cd107a336f1b7f13864e2f2cf94bd3a3f6","tid":1031642,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9da19fe38902ff0831e8fbf399efe0cae33521","tid":1031642,"uid":93062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"係咪因為有全內反射困住啲microwave<br />\n能量太大所以產生plasma"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"係,keep住resonance"},{"pid":"8426f31f761bdf699d6c59a4bb5baf1a7156b2ab","tid":1031642,"uid":22019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"條友揸機揸得咁撚衰"},{"pid":"4a8c1765e63bbbbd49073e1b77e15e623fff16f3","tid":1031642,"uid":8461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7f1c078ecf99e4ebcbe3a898a6fa217e0c54737b","tid":1031642,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"b91db122c344875d64dc5420d287b8271aa8bf81","tid":1031642,"uid":8461,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"3b6f9fcf0d07ab321c14bf731706d12746288372","tid":1031642,"uid":6290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"我想知係咩原因導致到佢地會做成internal reflection of waves <br />\n係咪因爲提子皮佢有特別既構造而可以reflect waves <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:06:18.000Z","msg":"你上面條友唔識亂咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nA grape is the right size and <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">refractive</span></span> index to trap microwaves inside it.<br />\n<br />\nReflection 同 Refraction 係兩樣嘢嚟<br />\nn=c/v<br />\n<br />\n簡單講因為velocity of microwave in medium 慢咗所以先會trap住microwave<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"唔關velocity事,情況應該係total internal reflection,唔關個velocity快慢事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:47:50.000Z","msg":"Specifically, <span style=\"color: red;\">that the effect is a result of aqueous dielectric objects displaying morphology-dependent resonances (MDRs) at microwave frequencies. MDRs are synonymous with Mie resonances, which describe the near-field effects of resonant interactions of light with wavelength-scale objects</span> (3, 4). The objects can be conductive or dielectric and absorptive or transparent, depending on the complex dielectric permittivity of the material. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2019/02/13/1818350116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2019%2F02%2F13%2F1818350116&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=c58cfcc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2019/02/13/1818350116</a><br />\n<br />\n睇曬成篇原文都無提及過total internal reflction<br />\n微波爐內部嘅microwaves 都好大機會係omnidirectional, 所以total internal reflection 未必成立<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki:<br />\nMie resonances describes the scattering of an electromagnetic plane wave by a homogeneous sphere.<br />\n<br />\n係有resonances<br />\n但report 話resonance 係由mie resonances 產生<br />\n無理解錯就應該唔係由total internal reflction 去 stack up<br />\n<br />\n關於皮嘅問題：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Apparently a grape's skin has nothing to do with it at all.</span> The authors were able to produce plasma using a simple pair of hydrogel beads as well as gooseberries, large blackberries, and even quail eggs. They concluded that lots of things about the size of a grape with sufficient water content can produce plasma as long as the two objects are less than three millimeters apart."},{"pid":"c3d7d1716e63cdedc8a49c293e80f455d285e8f8","tid":1031642,"uid":65328,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"講起等離子就諗返以前中學既事，<br />\n<br />\n我讀文科， 理科搞咗個常識比賽， <br />\n有一題就問第四形態係咩，我答等離子，主持話我錯， 應該係電漿。<br />\n<br />\n結果就係差果題既分搞到得第二"},{"pid":"9b6c80eef3fa911c12ec7f85aae2125b35154e6c","tid":1031642,"uid":97350,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"聽左好多次都唔明，點解明明wavelength 係12cm但入到微波爐會變左1/10? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c07b21bf5095664a753575b57273de99c4331e"